content.detailedDescription:
I live by the rock lake pyramids in lake mills wisconsin.

left my house to watch the blackhawks game at a friends house and notice a lightning storm to the south east.
grabbed camera and tripod and setup to take pictures at 9:27pm.
trees in the way so i moved east to the boat landing and setup.

at 9:56 i noticed a glowing orange ball headed west my way.
turned my camera on the tripod and took the first shot.
object instantly changed direction like it knew it was photographed.
i continued to shoot and captured 3 frames.

when i got home the flash drive would not read. corrupted.(log file attached)
i have had this camera a fuji finepix s5200 since 2005 and have never had drive problem.

i recovered the drive and the pictures. (attached)

i checked the star charts. nothing lined up. maybe aquarius / neptune. proved to be not.

many object in the pictures, looks like they are feeding or creating the thunder storm.
content.summary: While taking pictures of lighting. over the pyramids of rock lake. i observed objects. corrupted my flash drive. it specialist recovered drive.

content.detailedDescription: I was in my back yard trying to see the supernova in the pinwheel galaxy approximately 30 days after it was discovered.I was looking at the stars and saw movement in my peripheral vision causing me to look due west where i saw a single solid moving object  that passed directly over head and continued east at a constant speed and heading, so much that it stood out. i have seen a ufo or anything paranormal, so it was a shock.So when i first see it up to the point of passing over me my thoughts are wtf is that. i see 4 cubes in a straight line but moving as one they appear to be connected, there is a 5 th cube attached to the left side of the second cube.Now as the first part of this thing passes over head i see detail and it scared me, and i don't mean for my own safety, just in general as i was realizing that i'm witnessing something life changing, and i have a neural override where your brain shuts down non essential functions and doubles your visual audio and other sensory information uptake in an attempt at self preservation. it feels like the world around you is in slow motion. so from this point on the amount of detail i observed is sort of disturbing and 5 years later i can see it like it just happened. the detail,i type slow and i'm getting tired so i will condense but try to get every thing. it was non reflective and dark in color. the surface had some smooth areas the rest had raised and sunken lines with a lot of 90 deg turnes. my impression was conduit channels but they covered most if the surface like looking at a circuit board with light behind it, that dense and close together. the cubes turned out to be half as tall but square front to back and side to side. there was no lights or windows or obvious doors. it's movement was just forward but i have never seen anything move like it.The best i can describe it, absolute flawless.The bottom center of every square had a highly reflective circle that was about 1/3 the size of the square and as it moved overhead amber lights would move from the outside then cross the center to the far side of the circle but the light slowed way down as it crossed the center. i realized i was seeing amber street lights reflecting off black mirrored half spheres that were convex or concave. one would make light move fast across center the other slow. this was slow. i really would like to know if anyone has ever seen any thing like this. i would love to have somebody draw a pic of this, i've tried  but can't draw for sh you know what.My feelings were overwhelming i immediately tried to  debunk what i saw  as balloons or giant inflatable objects swamp gas. i started writing down details and tried to draw it.I didn't tell any one for  a long time not even my wife. if you want more detail you have my number text first so i will answer unknown number
content.summary: 4 large connected cubes in a row with a 5 th cube attached to left side of 2 nd cube on leading end

content.detailedDescription:
It happened a day after an airplane crash and it was very long and thin with points on either end very brillantly white, maybe glowed.

i remember the day very well because the day before we had an awful accident occur in our community, the blue angels number 6 plane had crashed on april 21 2007. on april 22 2007, the blue angels team performed again even after the crash had occurred. they performed as a salute to number 6. 

it was not long after the air show, i was in my bedroom and i heard jets flying around, i live very close maybe 2-3 miles from the beaufort marine corps air station, i thought maybe the blue angels were leaving, so i leaned out of my window and looked toward the direction i thought the jet was traveling.

that's when i seen the object. it was very thin and long, it looked like it come to a point at either end. it was very white or the thing its self was made of light, it was very bright against the brilliantly blue sky. 

my first reaction was to go outside and get a proper view, instead of having my upper body out the window, so i pulled myself out the window, and went outside, which took about 45 seconds and it was gone nowhere to be seen.

i thought it was very odd at first my father, sister, and boyfriend assumed that it was some sort of blimp by my description, but i know it was not a blimp it had no wings, no anything on it. it almost looked like a really thick line but pointed at either end. i have never seen anything like it before.

i was a seventeen year old girl at the time, i have always lived in a military town, i'm used to seeing aircraft off all sorts jets, the b52 stealth, helicopters, all different types just by living here i grew up watching the blue angels, they come every few years and perform. i have never seen a crash or that object before but neither were enjoyable. i am now twenty six.
content.summary: Glowing cigar shaped object, mid-day, day after blue angels crash.

content.detailedDescription: I walked outside with my wife to catch some fresh air. we always look at the stars outside as we are in a rural area. at first, the object appeared to be a large star. upon closer observation we noticed a shape and that the bright lights were part of a shape with other smaller lights along the edges. they were pulsing red, green, and some blue. we watched for over one hour then went inside. when i went out again to observe, approx., one hour later, the object had vanished.
content.summary: Boomerang shaped object sighted above rio verde foothills.

content.detailedDescription:
It was on feb 20, 2016 that the sighting occurred. it was the day the weather was going to change; a storm was rolling in from the west to end our summer weather week (in winter). it was in the early afternoon and my wife and i were sitting outside enjoying the view. our deck faces the ne. nne from our view points to gavilan mtn, fallbrook, ca, which we have a clear view of. the cloud front was just coming over us like a sea of grey and seemed to head in an ene direction. the leading edge of the clouds stretched out as far as we could see and appeared to be somewhat puffy and white with some holes that allowed you to see some blue sky behind them. there was a lower layer of a few thinner, stretched out clouds that you could see through that seemed to move in either an e or w direction, i don’t remember which, but i do remember it was at about a 30 degree angle to the direction of the storm front. i’d guess the layers were 100-300 feet apart. the biggest cloud of the lower layer intersected with the storm front and blue sky and that point appeared to be right over the top of gavilan and maybe 1,000 above it.

i had just made a sandwich, which was pretty messy. i was pretty hungry so i was eating it as i came out of the kitchen over to our outdoor sitting area. i was looking up at the sky in the area of where the two clouds met when something glimmered behind the leading edge of the storm clouds. i thought it was a plane above and behind the clouds that must have reflected the sunlight. but i couldn't see any object yet, although it still seemed to shine. then the object appeared to drift down below the storm layer, actually swinging like a pendulum in a grandfather clock. it was a very shiny/brilliant object, almost with a glow, and now i could make it out. it looked like a polished, whitish shiny barbell except the lower end of the “barbell”, or bell if you would, was dark and burnt looking. that end appeared to be behaving like parachuter would, dangling and swinging back and forth, and that was my first thought. odd though, both ends were relatively the same size which wouldn't be the case with a parachute. a parachute would have a much larger “chute” to carry the lower “bell”.  

at this time i glimpse a small plane maybe ¼ mile to the right of the object and i thought it must have come from that plane. then i realized the object was too high up to be associated with it. i still thought, since it was sort of floating down rather slowly, that either it would continue down and crash or the chute would have to open soon. either way i knew this wasn’t going anywhere for a while so i thought i’d put my sandwich down and grab my binoculars from the table behind me to check it out.  so i turned around, put my sandwich on the coffee table, picked up the binoculars and turned around and it was gone. i looked for hours and could never find a trace of it again.

the bar bell appeared to be 20-30 ft in diam. the “bar” appeared rectangular and shaded and was 8-12 ft rectangle maybe 30 - 40 ft long. the other dangling bell appeared dark, almost burnt, and actually looked like a square close to being 15 - 25 ft cube.

the area over gavilan mtn is not an area for parachuters and, although temecula often has balloonist, we have seen the balloonists much further off in the distance. i’m an engineer and i’ve worked for navy and i know this was not anything we have or will ever have.

yesterday i read mufon  case 74282. when i saw the cgi they have created representing what these men saw, i felt immediately that this is the same craft i saw several weeks earlier. i have included a jpg which i've cropped from the mufon file. the only difference i can immediately see from what i saw and the cgi is the dark edges in the cgi. however, when i viewed the object i saw it from an angle that made the darker edges unremarkable and one of the "bells" was black and square.

i’m an engineer and worked for the navy on several military aircraft. i've seen enough to know this wasn't any aircraft, swamp gas or anything normal. this was in broad daylight, close and large enough for me to identify, and high up enough in the sky for me to know that it should have still been there when i turned around.
content.summary: Barbell ufo drifting down through clouds

content.detailedDescription: I have terrible insomnia and got up to go outside on our patio (we live in an upstairs apartment, with a small covered patio on the south side) to smoke a cigarette. the patio is located outside my husbands office. the closer i got to the door, the more i felt like something was wrong. i shrugged it off and turned the handle. the feeling of something is not right swept over me and i hesitated. i finally went outside and was so creeped out that instead of sitting i leaned against the door to smoke. i realized that i couldn't hear anything , it was absolutely quiet except for a strange bird making noise. there is a very busy highway that is north east of us that you can hear the cars etc. at all times. there was nothing, not a single car could be heard. on top of that , there was no wind. it was dead still and silent. i was so creeped out that i noticed something coming overhead and at first i thought it was a walmart shopping bag, then realized that was impossible. i stared at the thing until i couldn't see it anymore. our apartment buildings are so close that by the time i ran in to grab my phone (which was all the way in the bedroom on the other side of the apartment) it would have been gone. about a minute after this thing passed, i could hear the cars on the highway again and even a small breeze. the object went at a slow speed overhead and seeemed to change shape almost unnoticeabely. it wasn't very bright and i'm not sure if the light was emitted or was reflected. before it dissapeared it looked as if it had black surrounding it but the center was still a yellowish color.
content.summary: When i first saw it i thought it was a walmart plastic shopping bag, but no wind

content.detailedDescription: April 11th i was sleeping in the rv vehicle i had rented, getting ready to leave for marfa, tx, in the morning. i got-up to walk my dog in the early hours, and while looking at the night sky, which had become clear, after a prior rain, i saw what appeared to be a star in the southern skies. but it slowly grew brighter, then emitted long, horizontal light rays, to the east and west, much like a flashlight, only a lot stronger, while the center light grew even brighter. then, the weirdest thing happened; something entered the light-ray to the east, and moved in front of the center, all the while, the light in the center was obscured like a passing train does, when moving in front of a light. the only thing that came to mind is; i was watching a 'space-train', connected craft transitioning through the light ray. i looked to see what my dog was doing, but when i looked back, the light rays were gone, then the 'star', blinked out. when i got back-in the vehicle, i looked at the time, it was 1:23 am, and the whole event had lasted only a couple of minutes. i had an incredibly hard time trying to verbalize this sighting.
content.summary: It looked like a train, passing in front of bright light

content.detailedDescription: I was traveling home and noticed bright amber stationary lights in the distance in a southerly direction on the night of april 28, 2015. i drove approximately 2 minutes and still found 4 stationary amber lights in a triangular formation. one amber light near the bottom of the triangle occasionally blinked. i was on a side road and began to turn up the road where the stationary lights/object was, i was approximately 150-200 ft from the object from beneath it at an angle. as i began to turn on the road it immediately accelerated from stationary to perhaps 45-50mph. this made me believe it was under some intelligent control, as it knew i was approaching it. i could not tell if there was a body connected to the lights. i first noticed the lights from the south and it proceeded in a ne direction where i eventually lost sight of it. as i continued down the road about 200-300 feet ahead i saw a stalled car on the side of the road with another car opposite of it looking like it was jump-starting the stalled car. i have never seen anything like this before and was shocked as to how rapidly the lights accelerated from being stationary. this occurred one year ago from tonight.
content.summary: Triangular ufo, hovering & fast acceleration

the only thing my brother told me, that he did not see the object when he took the picture. so i assume the ufo was invisible to the naked eye.

content.detailedDescription:
Was walking my dog and noticed a very bright, orange light low in the se. it seemed to move erratically. slightly "fluttering" in all directions as it moved e and actually passed between saturn and mars which were visible and low in the se sky at the time [slightly overcast as i could not see many dimmer stars, just the planets. little light pollution here so we usually can see many stars if it is clear]

i watched it for about 90 secs or so as it got lower in the sky as it moved e and eventually disappeared below the horizon.

the oddness of the very bright and clearly orange light was what first caught my attention. the strange, erratic movement and slight pulsating/morphing of the shape from round, was the detail that kept my attention. i am am amateur stargazer and know it wasn't a planet and immediately went in to check if it might be the iss or a satellite - neither showed up on my programs. there is a flightpath over this area, but they generally fly a different path and are easily distinguished. the slight overcast may have distorted the light/shape/movement.
content.summary: Very bright orange light, "fluttering", erratic but basically straight flight.

content.detailedDescription: Was a boomerang shape with translucent wings from a center oval shape with approx. 150 ft. wingspan and approx. 30 feet thick in center. wings had small winglets facing backwards. the object appeared in the se and moved in a direct path to the nw traveling slowly with no noise and no lights. object never deviated from its flight path appeared to have thicker leading edge with thinner trailing edge. there was trail or apparent exhaust from an engine or motor.
content.summary: Boomerang shape with translucent wings with winglets pointing backwards

content.detailedDescription: I had just come out of the rio hotel/casino to catch the e/b flamingo bus, i turned back toward the hotel because i caught this very bright white light out of my peripheral vision, it was going west, no sound, no blinking, or "faa" i.D. (anti-collision) light's, it glowed from within, no external light's. i am a former private pilot, and a aircraft & technology enthusiast, i am familiar with most kind's of aircraft, this wasn't a helicopter, or jet, or civilian aircraft, when i saw that it was returning e/b from behind the rio bldg. (on the left) i took out my cellphone to video it, took a picture then switched to video, (both included) i think it was a ufo, unless it was some kind of homemade drone, but from my best estimate it was about 300 ft.Alt. maybe 1/4 to 1/2 mile away, and looked to be about the size of a mini-van. i didn't see it emerge from behind bldg. #2, and right at that time my bus was arriving, you can hear it in the audio, along with traffic noise, so i had to stop the video (and further investigation) could you please take a closer look at it and let me know what you think, i don't have the equipment to enlarge the video to see more detail, i was very excited to observe this, and i think i got one! i believe that we are not alone, and have never been alone. . .And i hope i live long enough to experience "disclosure", and possibly meet, and interact with our space "family" thank you!!
content.summary: Saw object heading west, then coming back east, that's when i took the video. no faa light's, no sound, bright flourescent white.

content.detailedDescription: I realize it's been over 2 years since i saw the object, but it has stayed with me. i just discovered today how to report the sighting. i can remember it clearly. the date was february 22 2014. i know because my wife was scheduled to be induced the following morning to give birth to my son. i was outside getting some fresh air before going to bed. i enjoy looking at the stars and planets before bed. it helps me relax. i caught something out of the corner of my eye as i was looking up. i just noticed movement at first. i glanced over and realized there was something about to pass overhead, and i thought it was a large bird. i started to look away when i realized that there aren't many birds that fly at night, especially as large as this was. as i looked closer it was very black. i could see it because it was blacker than the night sky background, which made it stand out. as i watched it approach it looked like a piece of caution tape, but black instead of yellow. it almost looked like one of those spiral shaped wind chimes that was floating or being carried by the wind. as it passed overhead it made absolutely no sound and i was able to tell that it was a fixed wing craft. it had a boomerang/ chevron shape with an egg like dome or "cockpit." it was flying about 5-10 feet over the tree tops. i could definitely tell it was no bird at this point from the size. it's wingspan was about 8-10 feet across, about the length of an suv. it was very thin except for the "cockpit" bulge at the apex of the wings. it continued along in a straight line until i couldn't see it anymore. it never made a sound. i went inside to tell my wife, but she was going to give birth the next day and just wanted to go to sleep. she didn't want to hear about it then. in the morning i grabbed a pad and a pencil. i felt compelled to draw what i saw. i attempted the best i could  while my wife was being induced, but i could never quite duplicate it. she accepted that i saw something and could tell it was bothering me, so she let me draw while we waited for her to dialate. after my son was born, it was hectic but i still tried to draw what i saw without success. i can still see it in my head to this day.
content.summary: Observed a black winged object. shape was boomerang/chevron-like. no noise. low to ground. about the size of a suv.

content.detailedDescription: I was in my room at the clinic. i am a physician intensivist. he was lying on my bed and checking my phone. observe a light that suddenly appeared in the window. i thought it was a plane. i was much closer and more fixed. other nurses came to see me looking at the object. we were several witnesses. for 20 minutes we see the light. i went to the intensive care unit to evaluate one of my patients. upon returning, the object had disappeared.
content.summary: Bright and fixed object. he turned quickly.

content.summary: It was a bright green flash

content.detailedDescription:
Central ontario ufo/object sighting
nearest city/town: alliston, ontario

driving along hwy 89 east towards alliston near airport road when i noticed a plane contrail in my line of sight about 45 degs from the horizon. it was a beautiful sunny day, warm and relaxing drive.

all of a sudden i see a whitish grey oval object seem to be following the plane contrail just below the contrail and maybe a few miles behind the actual plane. i assumed it was another plane but about a minute later the object seemed to slow down and from my viewpoint clearly looked oval in shape as i watched it periodically while driving. it was clearly an oval disk type shaped object which now had really got my attention. i pulled off to the side of the road while keeping an eye on the object.

i put the car in park and from the time it took me to get out of the car to look at the object where i had seen it, it had vanished. maybe 3 to 4 seconds.

the interesting part of this sighting is that there was a break in the plane contrail roughly where i had seen the object last. it was as if the object stopped and punched upward through the plane contrail and disappeared altogether.

very cool experience. who knows what it was but i do believe in this type of phenomenon and what i had witnessed was truly astonishing.

thank you for reading. keep looking up!
content.summary: Whitish grey oval shaped disk

content.detailedDescription:
Filled out with witness on the phone at mufon h.Q. by field investigator l. flechtner on april 27th, 2016. i'm sorry i missed the time of event. l.F.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------


i looked up in the sky to see birds on the power lines and saw  three clusters of black circles, the three turned into five and were moving in a direct line path across the sky in a north to south direction. i could see the sky in between the circles, yet they seemed connected. they changed from a circle pattern to an arc like pattern, almost like some one threw a switch, and instantly they were changed. i did not see them move. then the pattern changed into a vee shape, or open triangle, then a wing shape, and then back to the circle. it never changed direction, kept a straight line path while it was changing, and moved consistently, never speeding up or slowing down. i could see no lights or hear any sound. i estimate the distance from the ground at 15,000 feet in the sky.
the wind was from the southwest, the temperature was 85 degrees, humidity was at 85%. a storm had just passed and the object was flying into the storm.
there is a airport near by, but i only see the airplanes take off and land.
i am very familiar with aircraft, and this was definitely not regular aircraft.
content.summary: I looked up in the sky to see birds on the power lines and saw  three clusters of black circles, the three turned into five and were moving in a direct line path
